[
  {
    "startTime": 6.2,
    "endTime": 7.800000000000001,
    "text": "An important room, this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.9,
    "endTime": 10.3,
    "text": "After all, it is a chocolate factory."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.4,
    "endTime": 12.3,
    "text": "Then why is the door so small?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.6,
    "endTime": 15.5,
    "text": "That's to keep all the great, big, chocolatey flavor inside."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.1,
    "endTime": 41.5,
    "text": "Now, do be careful, my dear children."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.6,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "Don't lose your heads."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.5,
    "endTime": 45.4,
    "text": "Don't get overexcited."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 49.4,
    "text": "Just keep very calm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.4,
    "endTime": 66.7,
    "text": "It's beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.4,
    "endTime": 68.30000000000001,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.4,
    "endTime": 71.80000000000001,
    "text": "Oh, yeah, it's very beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.6,
    "endTime": 87.39999999999999,
    "text": "Every drop of the river is hot melted chocolate of the finest quality."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.5,
    "endTime": 95.2,
    "text": "The waterfall is most important."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.3,
    "endTime": 96.89999999999999,
    "text": "It mixes the chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.2,
    "endTime": 100.0,
    "text": "Churns it up; makes it light and frothy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.5,
    "endTime": 107.7,
    "text": "And by the way, no other factory in the world mixes its chocolate by a waterfall, my dear children."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.8,
    "endTime": 109.6,
    "text": "And you can take that to the bank."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.9,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "People!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.14,
    "endTime": 131.3,
    "text": "Those pipes suck up the chocolate and carry it away all over the factory."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.7,
    "endTime": 133.6,
    "text": "Thousands of gallons an hour."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.9,
    "endTime": 134.70000000000002,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.8,
    "endTime": 137.3,
    "text": "And you like my meadow?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.4,
    "endTime": 138.9,
    "text": "Try some of my grass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.0,
    "endTime": 140.5,
    "text": "Please have a plate; please do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.6,
    "endTime": 143.6,
    "text": "It's so delectable and so darn good looking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.3,
    "endTime": 145.5,
    "text": "You can eat the grass?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.9,
    "endTime": 146.9,
    "text": "Of course you can."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.1,
    "endTime": 151.79999999999998,
    "text": "Everything in this room is eatable; even I'm eatable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.9,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "But that is called cannibalism, my dear children, and is, in fact, frowned upon in most societies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.1,
    "endTime": 158.9,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.4,
    "endTime": 161.20000000000002,
    "text": "Enjoy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.2,
    "endTime": 164.2,
    "text": "Scoot!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.0,
    "endTime": 186.9,
    "text": "Son."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.0,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "Please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.4,
    "endTime": 193.6,
    "text": "Dad, he said, \"enjoy\"."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.1,
    "endTime": 211.29999999999998,
    "text": "Why hold onto it? Why not start a new piece?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.8,
    "endTime": 213.60000000000002,
    "text": "Because then I wouldn't be a champion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.7,
    "endTime": 215.39999999999998,
    "text": "I'd be a loser like you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.3,
    "endTime": 247.20000000000002,
    "text": "Daddy, look over there!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.6,
    "endTime": 249.9,
    "text": "What is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.5,
    "endTime": 252.1,
    "text": "It's a little person!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.4,
    "endTime": 254.5,
    "text": "Over there, by the waterfall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.1,
    "endTime": 258.20000000000005,
    "text": "There's two of them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.3,
    "endTime": 259.5,
    "text": "There's more than two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.7,
    "endTime": 267.4,
    "text": "Where do they come from?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.6,
    "endTime": 268.70000000000005,
    "text": "Who are they?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.4,
    "endTime": 271.79999999999995,
    "text": "Are they real people?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.2,
    "endTime": 274.7,
    "text": "Of course they're real people; they're Oompa-Loompas."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.4,
    "endTime": 279.7,
    "text": "Oompa-Loompas?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.8,
    "endTime": 281.5,
    "text": "Imported direct from Loompa Land."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.6,
    "endTime": 282.6,
    "text": "There's no such place."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.3,
    "endTime": 284.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.5,
    "endTime": 288.5,
    "text": "- Mr. Wonka, I teach high school geography, and I'm here to tell you⏤  - Well..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.6,
    "endTime": 292.5,
    "text": "... then you'll know all about it and know what a terrible country it is."
  }
]